br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dw7Ng_YU8AAMAtf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDw7Ng_YU8AAMAtf.jpg&h=73a5065e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d047e2da74160e7455bba8c767322f209df1ae73","tid":1027480,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:24:44.000Z","msg":"安聯環球投資： 美中料將爆發科技冷戰，迫使其他國家選邊站<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-19<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯盧永山／綜合報導〕安聯環球投資（Allianz GI）表示，美國和中國就長期而言可能爆發科技冷戰，兩國有機會發展獨立的科技生態系統，從而禁止對方使用自身的供應鏈，迫使其他國家只能選邊站。<br />\n<br />\n　安聯環球投資亞太區股票首席投資總監陳致強指出，美中90天貿易談判期即將結束，預料美國尋求降低貿易逆差與智財權保護的訴求將會實現，但針對國有企業補貼等的中國經濟結構性議題則會處於膠著狀態，而科技問題最終會演變為科技冷戰。<br />\n<br />\n　陳致強表示：「市場應該預期最終會出2套科技生態系統，一方主要為西方國家，另一方是中國及部分新興市場國家，情況猶如2G時代的GSM與CDMA。」<br />\n<br />\n　安聯環球投資認為，美中兩國在當前的談判或許可達成貿易協議，避免關稅進一步提高，但雙方互不信任將加劇地緣政治緊張局勢，影響全球科技業供應鏈。<br />\n<br />\n　陳致強指出，中國靠著「中國製造2025」和「一帶一路」倡議等舉措，預計將繼續加強投資科技及其他相關產業的技術研發，中國的研發投資將很有可能於2020年超越美國。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;<br />\n<br />\n仲想透過香港白手套輸入西方高科技"},{"pid":"a9ffcf31ea61ae070eeafada63839903763c08a1","tid":1027480,"uid":56323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:27:22.000Z","msg":"講到尾又係拎香港黎搵水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家咁多支那股， 遲早收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c8cb76421e3c69f6f49ad03d7c9d5b19c350b1","tid":1027480,"uid":41308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a9ffcf31ea61ae070eeafada63839903763c08a1","tid":1027480,"uid":56323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:27:22.000Z","msg":"講到尾又係拎香港黎搵水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家咁多支那股， 遲早收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:32:24.000Z","msg":"香港收左皮好耐啦"},{"pid":"04813d56ddf663a44a32a123dee5fc69d30c281e","tid":1027480,"uid":41308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14f5eeb16b0362ee761867ef3e3923b524962ca9","tid":1027480,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d78118301a7008e8208dea58a47e5f4feaaae8d","tid":1027480,"uid":54733,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"bee7f6fa240b08193f3cd2b86089a26ac335adfb","tid":1027480,"uid":35790,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:02:58.000Z","msg":"美取消香港政策法<br />\n取消獨立關税區<br />\n及禁高科技輸港<br />\n即可玩完"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:05:22.000Z","msg":"中國仲要咁高調宣傳大灣區<br />\n睇下rubio/trump會點對香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:08:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:33:26.000Z","msg":"人地一早收晒風 做左野啦"},{"pid":"bf47b7ee11dd857249ca15f73e0d794b71d1b87c","tid":1027480,"uid":84128,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:33:56.000Z","msg":"創條閪咩<br />\n自己人都唔尊重自己友<br />\nIt狗前it狗後<br />\n想創科？<br />\n你移撚走哂班大陸落黎既低端人口咪創到"},{"pid":"d9d5767d5a876ec255b682caf2787a9adfbe458e","tid":1027480,"uid":41308,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8839ea379abefd3a57383d6dd8840ab513c868c7","tid":1027480,"uid":35790,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:04:45.000Z","msg":"香港融入大灣區 影響與美國關係？<br />\n<br />\n由中共中央成立的粤港澳大灣區建設領導小組8月15日在北京召開首次會議。外界一直懮慮，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港融入大灣區可能抵觸&ldquo;美國-香港關係法&rdquo;的條款。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgangtai%2Fgf3-08152018093855.html%2FampRFA&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpElcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=ca158993\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA</a><br />\n(殘體)<br />\n<br />\n美國會報告<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong continues on the path of greater economic integration <br />\nwith the Mainland. The Hong Kong government has sought to <br />\nposition Hong Kong as a regional hub for China&rsquo;s Belt and Road <br />\nInitiative and a key node of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau <br />\nGreater Bay Area integration project, Beijing&rsquo;s plan to establish <br />\na globally competitive advanced manufacturing, finance, and <br />\ntechnology center.<br />\n<br />\n報告摘要（英文）：<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnnual_Report%2FChapters%2FChapter&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpElcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=cdea1e22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter</a> 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf<br />\n[/url]<br />\n取消香港獨立關税區<br />\n取消香港護照免簽證<br />\n香港變成中國一個普通城市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:34:27.000Z","msg":"刁帝根本無諗過呢個問題，日日打飛機"},{"pid":"b2f4c911e4405f9f3dc3ca3c756d8bf59735ebf3","tid":1027480,"uid":74778,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:48:51.000Z","msg":"班仆街陷家剷大陸官仲要寫到個大灣區綱領係要香港<strong>繼續做乜撚野創新科技離岸乜撚野中心</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你要笑死唔笑死，香港不嬲都係比大陸當白手套，過橋偷外國技術，洗黑錢，跳板出國移民<br />\n<br />\n創新科技更加得淡笑，由董建華年代，數碼港到宜家都淨係識消費搵過steve job影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲大撚把新聞搵到數碼港科學園唔睇好既創科公司，係外國發光發熱，攞曬獎<br />\n<br />\n香港成個創科工業既funding都係用黎起樓，已經有數碼港科學園，宜家再係大灣區起<br />\n<br />\n香港政府有咩用？幫大陸政府通過d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64a4395373702dd4ab20740517f322fad720fbe3","tid":1027480,"uid":113929,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"吹到咁大，過2年又咪唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n千年大計， 雄安新區而家點"},{"pid":"083c80fbc1ac36084b874380d11984590f4f775b","tid":1027480,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201