7480,"uid":18955,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:20:50.000Z","msg":"中共吸取經驗<br />\n<br />\n以往大陸仆街香港有運行<br />\n現在大陸仆街拿拿抱住香港個救生圈<br />\n<br />\n一萬億儲蓄<br />\n拎住本特區護照對內自稱中國人<br />\n對外可享有前英屬香港嘅待遇<br />\n白手套公司 輸入禁運大陸嘅產品/科技<br />\n再偷運去大陸<br />\n<br />\n你地有幾耐無聽過東方之珠呢個名？<br />\n睇黎香港呢兩隻字被中共消費得七七八八<br />\n2019 年內取消香港政策法係極有可能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"特區護照個封面，中文就中國大過香港，英文就香港大過中國。<br />\n其實都暗示咗香港係用嚟做乜。　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n習近平一係蠢，想攪一番作為，乜都攪。但係從咩梁家河之後講得出嘅政績係 0 。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n煤改氣咁小事都一鑊粥，大灣區 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢唔係蠢嘅話，就係當香港係眼中釘。香港一國兩制晌佢眼中係令香港變成法外之地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為防止任何反自己嘅勢力，分分鐘溶解香港本身就係佢嘅 agenda 一部份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8bb5d8fdbecefcea543c4a29ee6011a013719bd","tid":1027480,"uid":34394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bee7f6fa240b08193f3cd2b86089a26ac335adfb","tid":1027480,"uid":35790,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:02:58.000Z","msg":"美取消香港政策法<br />\n取消獨立關税區<br />\n及禁高科技輸港<br />\n即可玩完"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:03:24.000Z","msg":"快啦屌，想睇啲建制派含撚，到時佢地肯定變反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432fa3ece36d3291042d0d950fc413a00540591c","tid":1027480,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8839ea379abefd3a57383d6dd8840ab513c868c7","tid":1027480,"uid":35790,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:04:45.000Z","msg":"香港融入大灣區 影響與美國關係？<br />\n<br />\n由中共中央成立的粤港澳大灣區建設領導小組8月15日在北京召開首次會議。外界一直懮慮，<span style=\"color: red;\">香港融入大灣區可能抵觸&ldquo;美國-香港關係法&rdquo;的條款。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Fgangtai%2Fgf3-08152018093855.html%2FampRFA&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpElcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=ca158993\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf3-08152018093855.html/ampRFA</a><br />\n(殘體)<br />\n<br />\n美國會報告<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong continues on the path of greater economic integration <br />\nwith the Mainland. The Hong Kong government has sought to <br />\nposition Hong Kong as a regional hub for China&rsquo;s Belt and Road <br />\nInitiative and a key node of the Guangdong-Hong Kong-Macau <br />\nGreater Bay Area integration project, Beijing&rsquo;s plan to establish <br />\na globally competitive advanced manufacturing, finance, and <br />\ntechnology center.<br />\n<br />\n報告摘要（英文）：<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FAnnual_Report%2FChapters%2FChapter&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpElcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=cdea1e22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uscc.gov/sites/default/files/Annual_Report/Chapters/Chapter</a> 3 Section 4- China and Hong Kong_0.pdf<br />\n[/url]<br />\n取消香港獨立關税區<br />\n取消香港護照免簽證<br />\n香港變成中國一個普通城市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:07:43.000Z","msg":"港爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ed5323da6d8311c3260f11b771aae4fcfcd463","tid":1027480,"uid":131441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:08:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35e6b0b4eeed71b55614fb04544a2765dc0c3fbe","tid":1027480,"uid":20815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T02:12:06.000Z","msg":"創新既基礎係自由，你憑咩